cu.explanation_en: Setting the tracking area code to a negative value will cause configuration validation error during startup, as tracking area codes must be non-negative.

du.explanation_en: Setting the tracking area code to a negative value will cause configuration validation error during startup, as tracking area codes must be non-negative.
du.explanation_zh: 將追蹤區域代碼設定為負值會在啟動期間導致配置驗證錯誤，因為追蹤區域代碼必須為非負數。
